{"tid":1218574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緩衝期開拓新戰線】適合各種單兵鍵盤戰士！","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:02:08.000Z","uid":122933,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef3283b65231d50454380f1cab584b531566371","tid":1218574,"uid":122933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"其實如果依兩日係備戰時期，<br />\n<br />\n個人淺見係應該發揮鍵盤隊嘅力量<br />\n利用fact check 嘅文字&amp;圖<br />\n<br />\n攻陷以下兩個地方：<br />\n1. 香討（開account)<br />\n2. Facebook 撐警留言<br />\n<br />\n我哋民意一定會慢慢咁流失<br />\n所以襯依家都應該令對面唔好過！<br />\n<br />\n～～～～～～～～集思廣益～～～～～～～<br />\n簡單步驟：<br />\n1. 開相關account(空號都得）<br />\n<br />\n2. 直接複製已Fact check 嘅圖+少量描述文字<br />\n-開post /留言都要做<br />\n- 選圖必須為有利風向嘅圖（發夢扔磚片就免）<br />\n- 愈精簡愈好<br />\n- 唔需要花喉舌同廢老急，一擊脫離去下一帖<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n一來資源文宣組已整好，<br />\n二來一擊脫離又唔影響自己心情。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，五毛戰術！！<br />\n<br />\n以其人之道還治其人之身"},{"pid":"932490e545fa7ccf97aeaac65f12de47cbd0c79f","tid":1218574,"uid":122933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"有建議歡迎提出<br />\n<br />\n認同&amp;有興趣的正評一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a7152494a392fcf2afc6b8c3e51cb0e5f4e901","tid":1218574,"uid":122933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d91f6541c5bbd46f16a4c61e62421734e2cfa8aa","tid":1218574,"uid":122933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bab4f4a34d24a75c2d2eed2449041c4b608e6558","tid":1218574,"uid":122933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"970ade4b88b93f5aca51f5976eba4d8e5e363c53","tid":1218574,"uid":113509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da312bb17755a4681b56ab8ead378895351d3cab","tid":1218574,"uid":4617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r